{
  "folder": "d0OxVZ6zGiVpmgRV",
  "name": "Deck Bond",
  "type": "deck",
  "description": "<p>This Path provides archetypes to represent the different kinds of people who may have had the most lasting impact on your character's life thus far. They could be important figures in a community, a passerby, a close acquaintance, or someone they have never seen in person. These can be as intimate and personal or as formal and distanced as you want. Someone can just as easily change your life from next door as they can from a world away! Keep distance in mind and whether this person is aware of your character or not. They may play a pivotal role in your story—but are you even a footnote in theirs? Perhaps not yet…</p>",
  "img": "modules/lazybobcat-generic-content/artwork/session-zero/bond/back.webp",
  "system": {},
